thinproxy (0.0.10-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * SO_SPLICE zero-copy relay for CONNECT tunnels on OpenBSD.
  * accept4(SOCK_NONBLOCK) on OpenBSD.
  * Cache time(NULL) per poll cycle.
  * Fix cross-platform build for macOS, Ubuntu, and glibc.

 -- Renaud Allard <renaud@allard.it>  Thu, 19 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000

